  <brief_title>Laparascopy Versus Laparatomy in the Management of Ruptured Ectopic Pregnancy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A RANDOMISED TRIAL COMPARING LAPARASCOPY VERSUS LAPAROTOMY IN THE MANAGEMENT OF WOMEN DIAGNOSED WITH ECTOPIC PREGNANCY</official_title>
  <sponsors>
